{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957970/extras/Chest.png?t=1738307719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compelled by a mysterious note, you step into the grand mansion. As you explore its dark corridors, you must solve cryptic puzzles, confront the residents, and uncover your purpose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SOMNIFUGE</strong> is a first-person indie horror game that\u00a0blends exploration, puzzle-solving and psychological horror. Drawing inspiration from the eerie atmospheres of <i>Silent Hill</i> and <i>Alone in the Dark</i>\u2014as well as the many indie horror games they influenced\u2014<i>SOMNIFUGE</i> calls back to PSX-era horror with its retro visuals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the creator of the well-received indie horror shorts <i>Burger &amp; Frights</i> and <i>Dreader</i>, <i>SOMNIFUGE</i> continues the tradition of atmospheric, surreal horror games with minimal dialogue.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The World</strong>: Explore the atmospheric mansion, the maze-like library, the twisting hospital ward and more cursed locations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzle Solving</strong>: Solve challenging puzzles.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survival</strong>: Meet the host of horrors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Controller Support</strong>: Full 360 controller support.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957970/extras/Tranquility.gif?t=1738307719\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2957970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738307719","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app